tiation and analysis (minimum 5 years) · Experience in leading, motivating and managing sales teams (minimum 5 years) · Preferably have a background in animal nutrition · Confidence in projecting results to board of directors · Proven experience in writing, executing and exceeding sales budgets that include clear objectives and sales outcomes · Excellent interpersonal and communication skills, both written and oral (Ideally Indonesian) · Intermediate to advanced computer skills including Microsoft Excel, Word, and OutlookTo find out more send your resume in word format to shannonw@austcorpexecutive.com.au or phone +61 2 8252 1110 for a confidential discussion.NB: All candidates that meet our client’s shortlist will be contacted!!! Please feel free to connect on Linkedin http://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=4634987&trk=myg_ugrp_ovrAbout this companyAustCorp ExecutiveAustCorp Executive offers executive search and tailored recruitment solutions across the Asia Pac region in three main areas: Executive Search, Advertised Selection and Contingency Search. We place top 5% executives in the following sectors: - Environmental & Carbon - Construction (Infrastructure & Buildings) - Water & Energy - Mining - Facilities Management & CRE - Oil & Gas - Professional Services - Manufacturing and supply chain - Medical and Life Science - IT & Digital Media Business functions we support (across all of our markets and sub sectors): - IT & ITC - Finance - Customer Service & Support - Sales and Marketing - Engineering - Operations - Production - Projects - OH&S - Human Resources - Management - Executive Leadership We recruit both permanent and contract roles. Our motto is ‘your people are your most powerful resource’. We believe that a recruiter who can make insightful decisions about people is a company’s best source of competitive advantage. This is why AustCorp Executive only works with clients whose businesses are growing, and who need a committed partner to provide a consistent strea